</p>

</div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-02-09-02-0261-fn-0001-ptr" id="GEWN-02-09-02-0261-fn-0001">1</a>

   <p><a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-02-09-02-0312" class="document">GW sent a letter to Sarah Bomford on 23 Dec. 1773</a> in the care of her husband Isaac.</p>

